  {
    "id": "f_csv_90d30d8c49",
    "slug": "laws-are-the-terms-by-which-independent-and-isolated-men-united-to-form-a-societ",
    "texto": "Laws are the terms by which independent and isolated men united to form a society, once they tired of living in a perpetual state of war where the enjoyment of liberty was rendered useless by the uncertainty of its preservation. They sacrificed a portion of this liberty so that they could enjoy the remainder in security and peace.",
